The Biggest Fintech Funding Rounds So Far This Year
Fintech is booming. According to data provider CB Insights, as of June, venture back fintech firms had raised more than $8 billion in funding so far this year, including $5 billion in the second quarter alone. Average deal size? About $18.5 million.
